# ==============================================================================
# 🧠 AOXCORE PROTOCOL - SUBMODULE SPECIFICATION
# Purpose: Management of external cryptographic and testing frameworks.
# Version: 1.1.0 (X-Layer & OZ v5.0 Optimized)
